casebody.data:
In the Matter of the Estate of Velimir Bajkig. Sofia Kangara et al.; Katerina Bajkig et al.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs, unless appellants procure the record on appeal and appellants’ points to be served and filed on or before January 5, 1960, with notice of argument for the February 1960 Term of this court, said appeal to be argued or stibmitted when reached. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, M. M. Frank, Valente and Stevens, JJ.
